                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2"> <locus target="#3v">ff. 3v</locus>l. 4-4v: Ṣalot za-ʾarwe mǝdr, “Prayer against the serpent”. <quote xml:lang="gez"> <locus target="3v">3v</locus>: በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አ፩፡ በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ጸሎት፡ ዘአርዌ፡ ምድር፡ በስምከ፡ አደክርን፡ ድንቃላሌን፡ የዎስፌል፡ …</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#00"/>
                           <desc> <locus from="46v" to="47v">46v-47v</locus>: Text on the commemoration of the death of the Apostles. </desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez"> <locus from="46v" to="47v">46v-47v</locus>: …ፍ፡ ዕለተ፡ አረፍቶሙ፡ ለሃዋርያት፡ አበዊነ፡ አመ፡ ለመስከረም፡ ባርተሎሜዎስ፡ አመ፲፡ ወ፪ለጥቅምት፡ ማቴዎስ፡ አመ፡ ፲ወ፰ለህዳር፡ ፊልጶስ፡ …</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note is crudely written and lists the day of the death of the Apostles. The red ink is partly faded away.
                        </item>
